sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Frontend
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database

    Note over User,db: Login

    User->>+fe: Enter email + password
    fe->>+API: POST /auth/login
    API->>API: Validate body (LoginUserSchema)

    alt Missing fields
        API-->>fe: 400 "Missing or empty required fields"
        fe-->>User: Show error
    else Valid input
        API->>+db: findUnique(user by email)
        db-->>-API: user or null

        alt User not found
            API-->>fe: 400 "Invalid username or password."
            fe-->>User: Show generic error
        else User found
            API->>API: bcrypt.compare(password, user.password)

            alt Password mismatch
                API-->>fe: 400 "Invalid username or password."
                fe-->>User: Show generic error
            else Password ok
                API->>API: jwt.sign({id, role}) — 7d expiry
                API-->>fe: 200 + Set-Cookie token<br/>(httpOnly, signed, sameSite=strict)
                fe-->>User: Store session, redirect to dashboard
            end
        end
    end

    Note over User,API: Logout

    User->>fe: Click "Logout"
    fe->>+API: POST /auth/logout
    API-->>-fe: 200 + Clear-Cookie token
    fe-->>User: Redirect to landing page
